    "description": "你被称为99，是唯一一位有资格参加漂移赛车比赛的人类驾驶员。在赛车机械天才乔治亚的协助下，你将随着赛季的推进，证明地球在漂移联赛中占有一席之地。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165510/extras/aef9220ef7fdb043c797eb904dbbee3c.poster.avif?t=1762780130\" width=616 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165510/extras/aef9220ef7fdb043c797eb904dbbee3c.webm?t=1762780130\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165510/extras/aef9220ef7fdb043c797eb904dbbee3c.mp4?t=1762780130\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>一个赛季是随机生成的，并且在多个星球上进行。在每个星球之间，您将有机会花费资源来修理或升级漂移赛车，并尝试进入最终比赛。在比赛之间，您还需要选择可能改变锦标赛进程的事件。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165510/extras/6c4ea2d70b112df6bb5ad829f80b99f0.poster.avif?t=1762780130\" width=616 height=191 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165510/extras/6c4ea2d70b112df6bb5ad829f80b99f0.webm?t=1762780130\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>通过每个赛季不断提高您的排名，您将获得新的漂移赛车、事件和模块，帮助您与最优秀的车手竞争并达到漂移联赛的顶尖位置。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165510/extras/93c77cc61ca796fa0304cc11d1d5ad85.avif?t=1762780130\" width=616 height=184 /></span>",
